name: Moniac Mod Archive 032627
description: The Moniac was being configured as an encryption device, and the unknown student gained access to it with the excuse of creating these prints which became quite popular. When the spy was discovered by MI6, the prints were confiscated and archived for the next 60 years.  These prints are the hand-numbered archived prints now being released to the public as Cold War artifacts and works of mod design in their own right.
